{"tid":531634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳太攀蛇毒液量破全球紀錄 一啖足夠殺100人","createTime":"2018-01-17T04:39:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-17T05:09:09.000Z","uid":13468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"475e1440f00181d25c03724092e55934bb6a652d","tid":531634,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T04:39:12.000Z","msg":"澳太攀蛇毒液量破全球紀錄 一啖足夠殺100人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n澳洲悉尼爬蟲類公園一條「太攀蛇」（Taipan Snake）打破全球「一口最毒」的紀錄，牠只須咬一口，便能釋放出逾3克毒液，毒性足以殺死100人。<br />\n<br />\n太攀蛇「Whiplash」足足有2.5米長，園方出動兩名工作人員為牠擠出毒液，結果牠一口就擠出3.1027克毒液，毒液量幾乎是一般毒蛇的一倍，刷新世界紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n公園負責人拉姆齊（Daniel Rumsey）表示，太攀蛇並非全球最毒毒蛇，但其攻擊性舉世聞名，每年都會有人被咬後死亡。他稱「Whiplash」非常危險，但「對太攀蛇而言能擠出如此多（毒液），確實令人驚訝。」<br />\n公園內的蛇每兩周便要擠一次毒液，園方會將毒液製成蛇毒血清，用來治療被毒蛇咬傷的患者。目前爬蟲類公園是全澳洲唯一為太攀蛇擠毒液並製造血清的機構，如果有人不幸被太攀蛇咬傷，一般需要3至4支血清才能解毒。<br />\n<br />\n拉姆齊直言：「沒有這些蛇，便不會有血清」，故「Whiplash破紀錄的貢獻，日後將會用來拯救人命」。<br />\n英國《每日郵報》  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180115/57698491\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180115%2F57698491&d=W5fWDhjqhJPaoiRY8dxCENibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=ef7dfd01\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180115%2F57698491&h=bdedd2d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180115/57698491</a>"},{"pid":"2822307cf59d6f3c2c4073b056bb9cb6ecdb6b2b","tid":531634,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T04:41:46.000Z","msg":"屌啦<br />\n一下咬到一百人呀"},{"pid":"87327def3977494cab254b7027596ba83f0c3eed","tid":531634,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T05:01:10.000Z","msg":"毒撚射3克可以殺幾多人"},{"pid":"8fd646d3d488f9a740d03851ea621956eeb36204","tid":531634,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T05:05:38.000Z","msg":"連登仔散播既毒氣可以殺幾多人"},{"pid":"4ef6015e31d9e1311be3e7fa3af1cc20b0520819","tid":531634,"uid":33612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T05:05:43.000Z","msg":"毒液量幾乎是一般毒蛇的一倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7bb5050918f621e0898b1892237c0b1c8c7ffa3","tid":531634,"uid":60366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T05:09:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wy_TB6onHVE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dwy_TB6onHVE&d=W5fWDhjqhJPaoiRY8dxCENibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=d756f875\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wy_TB6onHVE</a>"}]}